snippet.title: Jacksmith
snippet.description: Jacksmith Management game. Forge steel, build the weapons and send the troops to attack enemy units.

snippet.title: Deadswitch 2
snippet.description: Deadswitch 2 Action game. Lead your troops to victory using brutal weapons to destroy all enemy units.

snippet.title: Siege Knight
snippet.description: Siege Knight Shooting game. Your duty is to protect the castle against enemy units with all sorts of weapons and traps.

snippet.title: Heavy Weapons
snippet.description: Heavy Weapons Action shooter with 60 levels, 3 bosses and 32 weapons. Use speed and tactics to destroy the aliens.

snippet.title: Tequila Zombies
snippet.description: Tequila Zombies Fighting game. Kill all zombies and earn cash to buy new weapons to stay alive as long as possible.

snippet.title: Tequila Zombies 2
snippet.description: Tequila Zombies 2 Shooting game. Kill all the zombies each wave using your brute power and several weapons to survive.

snippet.title: Sift Heads Assault 2
snippet.description: Sift Heads Assault 2 Shooting game. Try to eliminate all enemy units using guns and all sorts of other weapons.

snippet.title: Mass Mayhem: Zombie Apocalypse
snippet.description: Mass Mayhem: Zombie Apocalypse Shooting game. Try to survive as long as you can using diverse weapons to kill all zombies.

snippet.title: Death vs Monstars 2
snippet.description: Death vs Monstars 2 Arcade shooter. Play the Death and kill all the monsters. Collect the coins to upgrade your weapons.

snippet.title: Bee Quick
snippet.description: Bee Quick Arcade action! Try to get as much honey as you can each level and avoid or destroy the wasps.
